Package main

Class Item

java.lang.Object
main.Item
All Implemented Interfaces:
Purchasable
Direct Known Subclasses:
DefenceTrainingEquipment, DefensiveCoach, InsaneFood, Nutritionist, OffenceTrainingEquipment, OffensiveCoach, Trainer
public class Item extends Object implements Purchasable
The Item class reprents the Purchasables at the Market which are not Athletes. Items can be used to increase the stats of an Athlete. Items implements Purchasable because Items can be bought and sold in the MarketScreen.
Author:
Stephen Huang, Jasmine Ong
